definition: Google, Internet company and search engine

sentences.english: Google can shut down its phone manufacturing operations, or sell it off.
sentences.chinese: 谷歌可以关停手机生产部门，或是再次将其出售。

sentences.english: Even the big brains at Google are stumped.
sentences.chinese: 即使是谷歌的天才们也被难住了。

sentences.english: And this is only Google to enterprise-class start.
sentences.chinese: 而这只是谷歌转向企业级的开始。

sentences.english: But both Apple and Google have plenty of financial muscle to prolong the fight.
sentences.chinese: 但是，苹果和谷歌两家公司财力雄厚，足以打消耗战。

sentences.english: And Google is the tortoise then?
sentences.chinese: 那么谷歌就是那只乌龟？

sentences.english: Google's natural impulse is to unleash its algorithms on this video content in order to search it.
sentences.chinese: 谷歌的本能是在影片内容上挥洒其演算法以利搜寻。

sentences.english: It has teamed up with several partners to develop its Google TV platform.
sentences.chinese: 它已经和其他几个伙伴合作起来开发谷歌电视平台。

sentences.english: Zuckerberg's youth has given Googlers some confidence.
sentences.chinese: 扎克伯格的年轻也给了谷歌信心。

sentences.english: No, you can see them by poking around Google Maps .
sentences.chinese: 不，你可以看到他们的洪学智就是围绕谷歌地图。

sentences.english: Google has its own take on the Net-connected television.
sentences.chinese: 谷歌有自己的需要对网络连接的电视。

sentences.english: You could also try using some for the advanced commands in Google.
sentences.chinese: 您也可以尝试使用一些先进的命令在谷歌。

sentences.english: This invention of cereal song adduce cries " hippo water platen ".
sentences.chinese: 谷歌举出的这个发明叫“河马水滚筒”。

sentences.english: Yahoo - Yahoo was the Google of 2000.
sentences.chinese: 现在的雅虎就是2000年的谷歌。

sentences.english: Publishing it also could endanger Google employees in China, she said.
sentences.chinese: 出版也可能危及中国谷歌的员工，她说。

sentences.english: Where else might Google put the money to work?
sentences.chinese: 谷歌可以把钱用在其他什么地方呢？

sentences.english: A case against Google could update antitrust law for the Internet age.
sentences.chinese: 指控谷歌可能为互联网时代修订反托拉斯法。
